            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-1" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:rwsdjp">Cyprus • All-Inclusive Resort</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-3" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:cbzfeg">Mediterranean Grand Resort</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:rwsdjo">The ultimate stress-free experience with everything from ceremony flowers to unlimited cocktails included in one fixed price.</p>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:5yxob6">
