      <div class="space-y-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:5yxo9e">
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:cbzfed">What is usually included in an 'All-Inclusive' wedding?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:rwsdji">Our all-inclusive packages typically cover the venue hire, ceremony fees, wedding breakfast (meal), drinks package, basic floral decor, and your personal wedding coordinator.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:cbzfdr">Can we still have a small all-inclusive wedding?</h3>
