          </summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/AllInclusiveWeddingsContent.astro:rwsdiw">Yes, we have all-inclusive packages designed for intimate groups of 10-20 guests as well as larger celebrations for 100+ people.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
